OL,3,CHeadteacher admits stealing more than
OL,4,C#15,000 from schools
OL,6,FA headteacher has been warned to
OL,7,Fexpect jail after he admitted stealing
OL,8,Fmore than #15,000 from two schools
OL,9,Fwhere he worked.
OL,11,FNeil Metcalf claimed to be using the
OL,12,Fschool money to pay companies for
OL,13,Ftheir services - but instead paid the
OL,14,Fmoney into his own account.
OL,16,FThe 51-year-old was head of St Anthony
OL,17,Fof Padua Catholic Primary School in
OL,18,FMossley Hill, Liverpool, between
OL,19,FSeptember 2017 and May 2022, where he
OL,20,Fstole #10,800.
