OL,3,CHeadteacher admits stealing more than
OL,4,C#15,000 from schools
OL,6,FHe then moved on to Our Lady's Bishop
OL,7,FEton Catholic Primary School, also in
OL,8,FMossley Hill, from September 2022
OL,9,Fonwards where he stole #4,960.
OL,11,FMetcalf, of Childwall, Liverpool,
OL,12,Fadmitted two counts of fraud by abuse
OL,13,Fof position when he appeared before
OL,14,FLiverpool Crown Court on 18 July.
OL,16,FHe had previously pleaded not guilty
OL,17,Fwhen appearing before Liverpool
OL,18,FMagistrates' Court in June.
OL,20,FMetcalf was released on unconditional
OL,21,Fbail until his sentencing on 19 August.
