OL,6,FJudge David Aubrey KC told him: "You
OL,7,Fhave pleaded guilty to serious
OL,8,Fmatters. They are offences of
OL,9,Fdishonesty where, in the judgement of
OL,10,Fthis court, there has been a gross
OL,11,Fbreach of trust.
OL,13,F"However, before the court passes
OL,14,Fsense upon you any judge would require
OL,15,Fa pre-sentence report.
